                        <TextBlock 
                                   FontSize="14" TextWrapping="Wrap" Foreground="White">
                            <TextBlock.Inlines>
                                Absolutely! We prioritize your safety by ensuring a clean and secure browsing experience. 
                                We only have one non-intrusive ad to cover server costs, and we continuously monitor and scan ads 24/7 to remove any suspicious content.
                            </TextBlock.Inlines>
                        </TextBlock>

                        <Label Content="3/ What makes My Covid Record the ultimate vaccine information system?" FontSize="20" FontWeight="Bold" Foreground="White"/>

                        <TextBlock 
                                   FontSize="14" TextWrapping="Wrap" Foreground="White">
                            <TextBlock.Inlines>
                                Before developing My Covid Record, we extensively researched existing systems and learned from 
                                their strengths and weaknesses. We carefully selected the best features and removed any shortcomings, 
                                resulting in a superior platform for managing your health records. Here's why we confidently 
                                claim to be the best vaccine information system:
                                <LineBreak />
                                <LineBreak />
                                <Run FontWeight="Bold" Text="Safety" /> : Our top priority is to provide a safe browsing experience, 
                                free from harmful content. Comprehensive Content: My Covid Record focuses exclusively on health records, 
                                offering a wide range of COVID-19 test and vaccine information. You'll find comprehensive records across 
                                various categories, ensuring all your health-related data is in one place.
                                <LineBreak />
                                <LineBreak />
                                <Run FontWeight="Bold" Text="Quality and Accuracy" /> : We ensure that all records are of the highest quality and 
                                accuracy. My Covid Record allows you to view and download your certificates in the best resolution 
                                available, ensuring clarity and readability.
                                <LineBreak/>
                                <LineBreak/>
                                <Run FontWeight="Bold" Text="Effortless User Experience" /> : Compared to other systems, My Covid 
                                Record offers faster loading speeds and a seamless streaming experience. You can easily access 
                                and download your records for offline use, making it convenient for reference or travel requirements.
                                <LineBreak/>
                                <LineBreak/>
                                <Run FontWeight="Bold" Text="Regular Updates" /> : We regularly update our database with the latest 
                                test results and vaccine information, ensuring you always have the most up-to-date records at your fingertips.
                                <LineBreak/>
                                <LineBreak/>
                                <Run FontWeight="Bold" Text="User-Friendly Interface" /> : Our intuitive UI and UX design make navigating 
                                My Covid Record a breeze for users of all backgrounds. Whether you're searching for specific records 
                                or exploring categories, our site is designed to be user-friendly and accessible.
                                <LineBreak/>
                                <LineBreak/>
                                <Run FontWeight="Bold" Text="Compatibility" /> : My Covid Record is optimized for both desktop 
                                and mobile devices, allowing you to access your health records anytime, anywhere.
                                <LineBreak/>
                                <LineBreak/>
                                <Run FontWeight="Bold" Text="Dedicated Customer Support" /> : Our customer support team is 
                                available 24/7 to assist you with any inquiries, concerns, or technical issues. 
                                We pride ourselves on providing exceptional support to ensure a smooth and satisfactory 
                                user experience. If you're seeking a reliable and secure vaccine information system, 
                                we invite you to experience VaxTrackNZ. Help us spread the word and bookmark our site 
                                to stay connected with the latest health updates.
                            </TextBlock.Inlines>
                        </TextBlock>

                        <Label Content="4/ Can't access My Covid Record? Here's what to do:" FontSize="20" FontWeight="Bold" Foreground="White"/>

                        <TextBlock 
                                   FontSize="14" TextWrapping="Wrap" Foreground="White">
