                                access. We continuously update the list of domains, so be sure to bookmark My Covid Record.net 
                                to stay informed.
                                <LineBreak/>
                                <LineBreak/>
                                Thank you for choosing My Covid Record, and please help us spread the word by bookmarking our site and sharing it with others.
                            </TextBlock.Inlines>
                        </TextBlock>

